  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK416">
<l>eṉaittāṉu nallavai kēṭka vaṉaittāṉu</l>
<l>māṉṟa perumai tarum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Let a man listen, never so little, to good (instruction), even that will bring him great dignity.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
